Package com.hakan.core.configuration.containers

Class ConfigContainer

java.lang.Object
com.hakan.core.configuration.containers.ConfigContainer
Direct Known Subclasses:
JsonConfigContainer, YamlConfigContainer
public abstract class ConfigContainer extends Object
ConfigContainer is an abstract class that is used to load and save config files.
